WEBVTT

00:00:00.171 --> 00:00:04.440
Leading geographically dispersed teams introduces friction known as social distance.

00:00:05.322 --> 00:00:10.253
The split framework serves as a diagnostic tool for identifying the root causes of this friction.

00:00:11.035 --> 00:00:19.650
You must analyze structure, process, language, identity, and technology to pinpoint exactly where the systemic breakdown is occurring.
